{"id":794,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":794,"title":"Jeremiah 25","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 25"],[".studySummary",["i","Captive Judah will serve Babylon for seventy years—Various nations will be overthrown—In the last days, all the inhabitants of the earth will be at war."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.1","order":"02.25.025.52511"},["b","1"],"The word that came to Jeremiah concerning all the people of Judah in the fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah king of Judah, that",["i","was"],"the first year of Nebuchadrezzar king of Babylon;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.2","order":"02.25.025.52512"},["b","2"],"The which Jeremiah the prophet spake unto all the people of Judah, and to all the inhabitants of Jerusalem, saying,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.3","order":"02.25.025.52513"},["b","3"],"From the thirteenth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"year"],"of Josiah the son of Amon king of Judah, even unto this day, that",["i","is"],"the three and twentieth year, the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath come unto me, and I have spoken unto you, rising early and speaking; but ye have not hearkened."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.4","order":"02.25.025.52514"},["b","4"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath sent unto you all his servants the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"prophets"],", rising early and sending",["i","them;"],"but ye have not hearkened, nor inclined your ear to hear."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.5","order":"02.25.025.52515"},["b","5"],"They said, Turn ye again now every one from his evil way, and from the evil of your doings, and dwell in the land that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath given unto you and to your fathers for ever and ever:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.6","order":"02.25.025.52516"},["b","6"],"And go not after other gods to serve them, and to worship them, and provoke me not to anger with the works of your hands; and I will do you no hurt."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.7","order":"02.25.025.52517"},["b","7"],"Yet ye have not hearkened unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; that ye might provoke me to anger with the works of your hands to your own hurt."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.8","order":"02.25.025.52518"},["b","8"],"¶Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; Because ye have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"heard"],"my words,"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.9","order":"02.25.025.52519"},["b","9"],"Behold, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"send"],"and take all the families of the north, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Nebuchadrezzar"],"the king of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"Babylon"],", my servant, and will bring them against this land, and against the inhabitants thereof, and against all these nations round about, and will utterly",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"destroy"],"them, and make them an astonishment, and an hissing, and perpetual desolations."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.10","order":"02.25.025.52520"},["b","10"],"Moreover I will take from them the voice of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"mirth"],", and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom, and the voice of the bride, the sound of the millstones, and the light of the candle."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.11","order":"02.25.025.52521"},["b","11"],"And this whole land shall be a desolation,",["i","and"],"an astonishment; and these nations shall serve the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"king"],"of Babylon",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"seventy"],"years."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.12","order":"02.25.025.52522"},["b","12"],"¶And it shall come to pass, when",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"seventy"],"years are accomplished,",["i","that"],"I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"punish"],"the king of Babylon, and that nation, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", for their iniquity, and the land of the Chaldeans, and will make it perpetual desolations."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.13","order":"02.25.025.52523"},["b","13"],"And I will bring upon that land all my words which I have pronounced against it,",["i","even"],"all that is written in this book, which Jeremiah hath prophesied against all the nations."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.14","order":"02.25.025.52524"},["b","14"],"For many nations and great kings shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"serve themselves of them"],"also: and I will recompense them according to their deeds, and according to the works of their own hands."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.15","order":"02.25.025.52525"},["b","15"],"¶For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel unto me; Take the wine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"cup"],"of this fury at my hand, and cause all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"nations"],", to whom I send thee, to drink it."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.16","order":"02.25.025.52526"},["b","16"],"And they shall drink, and be moved, and be mad, because of the sword that I will send among them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.17","order":"02.25.025.52527"},["b","17"],"Then took I the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"cup"],"at the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s hand, and made all the nations to drink, unto whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had sent me:"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.18","order":"02.25.025.52528"},["b","18"],["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"To wit"],","],"Jerusalem, and the cities of Judah, and the kings thereof, and the princes thereof, to make them a desolation, an astonishment, an hissing, and a curse; as",["i","it is"],"this day;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.19","order":"02.25.025.52529"},["b","19"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Pharaoh"],"king of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Egypt"],", and his servants, and his princes, and all his people;"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.20","order":"02.25.025.52530"},["b","20"],"And all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"mingled"],"people, and all the kings of the land of Uz, and all the kings of the land of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"Philistines"],", and Ashkelon, and Azzah, and Ekron, and the remnant of Ashdod,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.21","order":"02.25.025.52531"},["b","21"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Edom"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"Moab"],", and the children of Ammon,"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.22","order":"02.25.025.52532"},["b","22"],"And all the kings of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Tyrus"],", and all the kings of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"Zidon"],", and the kings of the isles which",["i","are"],"beyond the sea,"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.23","order":"02.25.025.52533"},["b","23"],"Dedan, and Tema, and Buz, and all",["i","that are"],"in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"utmost"],"corners,"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.24","order":"02.25.025.52534"},["b","24"],"And all the kings of Arabia, and all the kings of the mingled people that dwell in the desert,"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.25","order":"02.25.025.52535"},["b","25"],"And all the kings of Zimri, and all the kings of Elam, and all the kings of the Medes,"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.26","order":"02.25.025.52536"},["b","26"],"And all the kings of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"north"],", far and near, one with another, and all the kingdoms of the world, which",["i","are"],"upon the face of the earth: and the king of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"Sheshach"],"shall drink after them."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.27","order":"02.25.025.52537"},["b","27"],"Therefore thou shalt say unto them, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, the God of Israel; Drink ye, and be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"drunken"],", and spue, and fall, and rise no more, because of the sword which I will send among you."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.28","order":"02.25.025.52538"},["b","28"],"And it shall be, if they refuse to take the cup at thine hand to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"drink"],", then shalt thou say unto them, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; Ye shall certainly drink."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.29","order":"02.25.025.52539"},["b","29"],"For, lo, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"begin"],"to bring evil on the city which is called by my name, and should ye be utterly unpunished? Ye shall not be unpunished: for I will call for a sword upon all the inhabitants of the earth, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.30","order":"02.25.025.52540"},["b","30"],"Therefore prophesy thou against them all these words, and say unto them, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall roar from on high, and utter his voice from his holy habitation; he shall mightily",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"roar"],"upon his habitation; he shall give a shout, as they that tread",["i","the grapes,"],"against all the inhabitants of the earth."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.31","order":"02.25.025.52541"},["b","31"],"A noise shall come",["i","even"],"to the ends of the earth; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"controversy"],"with the nations, he will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"plead"],"with all flesh; he will give them",["i","that are"],"wicked to the sword, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.32","order":"02.25.025.52542"},["b","32"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, Behold, evil shall go forth from nation to nation, and a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"whirlwind"],"shall be raised up from the coasts of the earth."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.33","order":"02.25.025.52543"},["b","33"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"slain"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall be at that day from",["i","one"],"end of the earth even unto the",["i","other"],"end of the earth: they shall not be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"lamented"],", neither gathered, nor",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_33c"},"buried"],"; they shall be dung upon the ground."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.34","order":"02.25.025.52544"},["b","34"],"¶Howl, ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"shepherds"],", and cry; and wallow yourselves",["i","in the ashes,"],"ye principal of the flock: for the days of your slaughter and of your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"dispersions"],"are accomplished; and ye shall fall like a pleasant vessel."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.35","order":"02.25.025.52545"},["b","35"],"And the shepherds shall have no way to flee, nor the principal of the flock to escape."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.36","order":"02.25.025.52546"},["b","36"],"A voice of the cry of the shepherds, and an howling of the principal of the flock,",["i","shall be heard:"],"for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath spoiled their pasture."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.37","order":"02.25.025.52547"},["b","37"],"And the peaceable habitations are cut down because of the fierce anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.38","order":"02.25.025.52548"},["b","38"],"He hath forsaken his covert, as the lion: for their land is desolate because of the fierceness of the oppressor, and because of his fierce anger."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.3a","order":"02.25.025.52549"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.2"},"Jer. 1:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/36.2"},"36:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.4a","order":"02.25.025.52551"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/26.5"},"Jer. 26:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.19.13-19"},"1 Ne. 1:19 (13–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.8a","order":"02.25.025.52553"},["b","8a"],["span.small","OR"],"obeyed."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.9a","order":"02.25.025.52555"},["b","9a"],["span.small","IE"],"send for."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.9b","order":"02.25.025.52557"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/43.10"},"Jer. 43:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.9c","order":"02.25.025.52559"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-bondage-of-in-other-lands"},"TG Israel, Bondage of, in Other Lands"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.9d","order":"02.25.025.52561"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.2"},"2 Kgs. 24:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.10a","order":"02.25.025.52563"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.34"},"Jer. 7:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/16.9"},"16:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.11a","order":"02.25.025.52565"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/28.14"},"Jer. 28:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.11b","order":"02.25.025.52567"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/29.10"},"Jer. 29:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.12a","order":"02.25.025.52569"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/36.21"},"2 Chr. 36:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/9.2"},"Dan. 9:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.12b","order":"02.25.025.52571"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/5.26"},"Dan. 5:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.14a","order":"02.25.025.52573"},["b","14a"],["span.small","OR"],"enslave them."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.15a","order":"02.25.025.52575"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.17"},"Isa. 51:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.21"},"Lam. 4:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/23.31"},"Ezek. 23:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.17"},"2 Ne. 8:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.26"},"Mosiah 3:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.17"},"D&C 29:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.15b","order":"02.25.025.52577"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.5"},"Jer. 1:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.1"},"46:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.17a","order":"02.25.025.52579"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.23"},"Isa. 51:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.18a","order":"02.25.025.52581"},["b","18a"],["span.small","OR"],"Namely."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.19a","order":"02.25.025.52583"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.25.2,25"},"Jer. 46:25 (2, 25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.19b","order":"02.25.025.52585"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.1"},"Isa. 19:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/29.2"},"Ezek. 29:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.20a","order":"02.25.025.52587"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.37"},"Jer. 50:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.20b","order":"02.25.025.52589"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/47.1"},"Jer. 47:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.21a","order":"02.25.025.52591"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.26"},"Jer. 9:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/27.3"},"27:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.7"},"49:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.21b","order":"02.25.025.52593"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.1"},"Jer. 48:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.22a","order":"02.25.025.52595"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/47.4"},"Jer. 47:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.22b","order":"02.25.025.52597"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/23.4.4-12"},"Isa. 23:4 (4–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/28.21"},"Ezek. 28:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.23a","order":"02.25.025.52599"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.26"},"Jer. 9:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.26a","order":"02.25.025.52601"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.9"},"Jer. 50:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.26b","order":"02.25.025.52603"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.41"},"Jer. 51:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.27a","order":"02.25.025.52605"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.26"},"Jer. 48:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.28a","order":"02.25.025.52607"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.16"},"Obad. 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.29a","order":"02.25.025.52609"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/9.6"},"Ezek. 9:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.30a","order":"02.25.025.52611"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.16"},"Joel 3:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.2"},"Amos 1:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.31a","order":"02.25.025.52613"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.1"},"Hosea 4:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.31b","order":"02.25.025.52615"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16"},"Isa. 66:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.22"},"Ezek. 38:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2"},"Joel 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.32a","order":"02.25.025.52617"},["b","32a"],["span.small","OR"],"storm."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.33a","order":"02.25.025.52619"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16"},"Isa. 66:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.33b","order":"02.25.025.52621"},["b","33b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],"."],["div",{"id":"33c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.33c","order":"02.25.025.52623"},["b","33c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/8.2"},"Jer. 8:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.34a","order":"02.25.025.52625"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/23.1"},"Jer. 23:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.34b","order":"02.25.025.52627"},["b","34b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.19"},"Ezek. 36:19"],"."]]}
